@moniquejaques first travelled to Gaza five years ago to cover an eight-day war between Israeli Defence Forces and Hamas. She's returned again and again to document the strength, creativity and vibrancy of Palestinian girls and young women. "There may be bombs dropping and power cuts, but the women of Gaza still get married, record songs, surf and ride horses," she says. 
