@oddman1969 took this photo of a displaced Iraqi woman waiting with her cat for transport in the village of Shaqouli, about 35km east of Mosul. She fled her home in the embattled city with her children to a camp in Arbil. As Islamic State loses control of areas in and around Mosul, summary executions and forced marches of civilians have become a grim feature.

